# Instructions for running the scenarios

1. Start Pox controller (cd pox, ./pox.py)

2. Run Python Topo script (sudo python Topo4s-4h.py)
This will run topology, ethtool, install tables, all the thing in run-bash script

3. from mininet, open xterm for h1 h2 h4, run their script h1.sh...
This will start all the snoop commands and Iperf commands